1. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing and specifically with Part-of-Speech tagging. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also a likely category as the paper discusses an unsupervised approach to POS tagging, which involves clustering and pattern recognition. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with a fundamental task in NLP and proposes an AI-based approach to solve it. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possible category as the paper may involve the use of neural networks or evolutionary algorithms in the unsupervised POS tagging approach. 
5. cs.SD (Software Engineering) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper may discuss the implementation and optimization of the proposed approach.
